---
// src/components/Confianza.astro
---
<section id="experiencia" class="py-24 px-6 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-4 tracking-tight uppercase">Seguridad Jurídica y Compromiso</h2>
            <div class="w-24 h-1.5 bg-indigo-600 mx-auto rounded-full"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 lg:gap-8">
            
            <div class="bg-indigo-950 p-10 rounded-[3rem] shadow-xl flex flex-col items-center text-center transition-transform hover:-translate-y-2 duration-300 min-h-[400px]">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-amber-400 mb-8 border border-white/10">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"></path></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-white mb-6 tracking-[0.15em] uppercase">Estrategia Procesal</h3>
                <p class="text-indigo-200 text-sm leading-relaxed font-medium italic">
                    "Contamos con amplia trayectoria en los Tribunales de CABA, aplicando soluciones creativas a conflictos patrimoniales complejos."
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-indigo-950 p-10 rounded-[3rem] shadow-xl flex flex-col items-center text-center transition-transform hover:-translate-y-2 duration-300 border-2 border-indigo-500/30 min-h-[400px]">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-amber-400 mb-8 border border-white/10">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle><path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"></path></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-white mb-6 tracking-[0.15em] uppercase">Respaldo Profesional</h3>
                <p class="text-indigo-200 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6 font-medium">
                    Ejercicio ético y profesional del derecho, brindando seguridad jurídica en cada etapa del proceso judicial.
                </p>
                <div class="mt-auto pt-4 px-4 py-3 bg-indigo-500/20 rounded-xl text-[10px] text-indigo-300 font-black tracking-[0.15em] uppercase border border-indigo-400/20 leading-relaxed">
                    Dr. Santibáñez Héctor David <br/> T° 124 - F° 535 CPACF
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-indigo-950 p-10 rounded-[3rem] shadow-xl flex flex-col items-center text-center transition-transform hover:-translate-y-2 duration-300 min-h-[400px]">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-amber-400 mb-8 border border-white/10">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"></path></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-white mb-6 tracking-[0.15em] uppercase">Reserva Absoluta</h3>
                <p class="text-indigo-200 text-sm leading-relaxed font-medium">
                    Garantizamos la máxima confidencialidad en el manejo de la información personal y patrimonial de nuestros clientes.
                </p>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</section>